resources.string:
This is the instruction for the subject before doing the test. Please read it carefully!

 Please make sure that you base your rating on your experience and not on the content that you were shown. Each time a sequence is shown, you should judge its quality by using one of the five levels of the following scale:

 				5: Excellent
 				4: Good
 				3: Fair
 				2: Poor
 				1: Bad
